      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, affordable, and full of potential, this vehicle is a smart choice for a budget-conscious buyer looking for dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It shows its age and wear, but it\u2019s being offered with clear value in mind by a seller committed to straightforward representation. A great low-cost option for someone who recognizes opportunity when they see it.",
