    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little budget-friendly car that\u2019s ready for someone who needs cheap wheels or a fun project to tinker with. It\u2019s not trying to be perfect, but it\u2019s got plenty of potential and could be a great fit for a handy buyer looking for value without spending big. If you want something straightforward, affordable, and worth a look, this one could be just the ticket.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a tough, no-nonsense character. Starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with a drivetrain that feels serviceable and a chassis that still has usable life left for someone who wants dependable point-A-to-B transportation or a platform to sort and improve over time. Cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and needed attention are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. Great candidate for a handy owner looking for affordable wheels with mechanical upside.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap ride. Runs, drives, gets the job done. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. Great beater, starter project, or parts car.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, well-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that\u2019s been out in the world collecting stories instead of sitting still. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly ride with personality, whether you need a practical daily, a weekend project, or a dependable set of wheels to keep life moving. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that makes it feel approachable, useful, and full of possibility for its next chapter.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It shows its age and is best suited for someone looking for an inexpensive daily driver, starter car, or project opportunity. A straightforward value play with room to make it your own.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone handy, a first-time buyer on a budget, or anyone after a practical runabout/project. It\u2019s priced fairly, has lots of usable life left for the right owner, and could be a really rewarding buy if you don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. If you want honest value without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid budget driver with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting transmission, and a chassis that still feels composed on the road. Not a cream-puff cosmetically, but the core mechanicals show good bones and it has the kind of simple, serviceable setup that makes a great commuter, backup car, or light project. Starts up, moves out well, and offers a lot of usable car for the money. If you want dependable basic transportation with room to tidy as you go, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
